      "content": "I'm not really following the dungeon or pantry analogies, I just need to focus on the technical requirements. To avoid that \"suffocating\" feeling, what specific weave structures would you recommend? Would a sateen weave be too dense compared to a traditional percale, or is there a better way to maintain that high thread count while ensuring the fabric stays breathable?",
